jodd.util

Class LoopIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • jodd.util.LoopIterator

  • public class LoopIterator
extends java.lang.Object
    Loop iterator that provides various counting data about the loop cycles. Should be used as in while construct: 
    
 while (loopIterator.next()) {
                // do something
 }
